#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:5 ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:46
#: 0f7ebd8c45714fd68ddc564b1329ad9f b7c25066fea445fb8cd1972f6d6f5b68
msgid "Signing In"
msgstr "登录"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:7 db561c137a2f45cf960137423f0ee731
msgid ""
"Before working with Telegram's API, you need to get your own API ID and "
"hash:"
msgstr ""
"在使用 Telegram's API 之前，你需要获得你自己的 api_id 和 api_hash："

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:9 3b125301e1fa40b89683b6bfe874a726
msgid ""
"`Login to your Telegram account <https://my.telegram.org/>`_ with the "
"phone number of the developer account to use."
msgstr ""
"使用你的手机号 `登录你的 Telegram 账号 <https://my.telegram.org/>`_"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:12 eef6f22c1b454e069e129f69cd4f9af1
msgid "Click under API Development tools."
msgstr "点击 API development tools"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:14 ba0a41b616394651b9a89f312c0240b3
msgid ""
"A *Create new application* window will appear. Fill in your application "
"details. There is no need to enter any *URL*, and only the first two "
"fields (*App title* and *Short name*) can currently be changed later."
msgstr ""
"一个 *Create new application* 窗口将会出现。你无需输入任何 *URL*，"
"目前只有前两个字段（*App title* 和 *Short name*）可以在后续修改。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:18 3041173dd69142f2a4fda961798a21d7
msgid ""
"Click on *Create application* at the end. Remember that your **API hash "
"is secret** and Telegram won't let you revoke it. Don't post it anywhere!"
msgstr ""
"点击页面底部的 *Create application*。记住你的 API hash 是保密信息。"
"而且 Telegram 不允许你重新生成它。切勿将其发布到任何地方！"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:24 059eb8d82d3548e3bf779cba8bd0f072
msgid ""
"This API ID and hash is the one used by *your application*, not your "
"phone number. You can use this API ID and hash with *any* phone number or"
" even for bot accounts."
msgstr ""
"此 API ID 和 hash 是用于*你的应用程序*，不仅限于你的手机号码。"
"你可以用这个 API ID 和 hash 登录*任何*手机号甚至bots。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:30 62a6fbe328ca49d6b0a0f0e1d50447f8
msgid "Editing the Code"
msgstr "如何编写代码"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:32 09083a133fdd45e6ae1fad5f1aa27220
msgid ""
"This is a little introduction for those new to Python programming in "
"general."
msgstr ""
"这是一个给 Python 编程新手的简单教程。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:34 d87f13b10a92406082afc6e2b80688ac
msgid ""
"We will write our code inside ``hello.py``, so you can use any text "
"editor that you like. To run the code, use ``python3 hello.py`` from the "
"terminal."
msgstr ""
"我们将把代码写在一个 ``hello.py`` 文件里，你可以使用任何你喜欢的文本编辑器。"
"要运行代码，请在终端中使用 ``python3 hello.py``"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:40 2389bf1580144321bcb2fcf0440f0113
msgid ""
"Don't call your script ``grammers.py``! Python will try to import the "
"client from there and it will fail with an error such as \"ImportError: "
"cannot import name 'Client' ...\"."
msgstr ""
"不要将你的脚本命名为 ``grammers.py``！Python 会尝试从那里导入 Client，"
"但程序会失败，并输出像这样的错误提示: \"ImportError: cannot import name 'Client' ...\"。”"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:48 eefb21fd8cf44447b61a52601e0582b0
msgid "We can finally write some code to log into our account!"
msgstr "现在我们终于可以编写一些代码来登录我们的账户了！"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:67 a22b47accc5042ed873193b3d49cb0b6
msgid ""
"In the first line, we import the class name so we can create an instance "
"of the client. Then, we define variables to store our API ID and hash "
"conveniently."
msgstr ""
"在第一行，我们导入了类名，这样就能创建一个客户端实例了。"
"然后，我们定义了一些变量来方便地存储我们的 API ID 和 hash。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:71 1184f1cb59164c02b8229d12d9ff3046
msgid ""
"At last, we create a new `Client <grammers.Client>`_ instance and "
"call it ``client``. We can now use the client variable for anything that "
"we want, such as sending a message to ourselves."
msgstr ""
"最后，我们创建了一个新的 `Client <grammers.Client>`_ 实例，并将其命名为 ``client``。"
"现在，我们可以将这个 client 变量用于任何我们想要使用的目的，比如向自己发送消息。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:77 9d282d6b7a0f46759a0abcf3f5e6dcd8
msgid ""
"Since Grammers is an asynchronous library, you need to ``await`` "
"coroutine functions to have them run (or otherwise, run the loop until "
"they are complete). In this tiny example, we don't bother making an "
"``async def main()``."
msgstr ""
"由于 grammers-python 是一个异步库，所以您需要使用 ``await`` 关键字来调用协程函数，"
"以使它们得以运行。在这个简单的示例中，我们编写了一个 ``async def main()`` 函数。”

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:82 559e6a87e30c44579f210407d9eb95f7
msgid "See :ref:`mastering-asyncio` to find out more."
msgstr "查看 :ref:`mastering-asyncio` 了解更多。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:85 b2be367293b4496dabb45c574fe09470
msgid ""
"If the ``.session`` file already existed, it will not login again, so be "
"aware of this if you move or rename the file!"
msgstr ""
"如果 ``.session`` 文件存在且有效，就不需要进行重新登录，"
"所以如果你要移动或重命名这个文件就需要注意这一点。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:90 c76ab68a33864978ba7a184d926c0157
msgid "Signing In as a Bot Account"
msgstr "登录 Bot 账号"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:92 d0a0570662104c549364ba7ccadf481a
msgid ""
"You can also use Grammers for your bots (normal bot accounts, not users)."
" You will still need an API ID and hash, but the process is very similar:"
msgstr ""
"你也可以使用 grammers 登录你的 bots (普通bot账号，而非用户账号)。"
"你依然需要 API ID 和 hash，但程序非常相似："

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:118 e7f842f0a2a04acf8c173c28eaec03b5
msgid ""
"To get a bot account, you need to talk with `@BotFather "
"<https://t.me/BotFather>`_."
msgstr ""
"要获取机器人账号，您需要与 `@BotFather <https://t.me/BotFather>`_ 进行交流。"

#: ../../source/basic/signing-in.rst:123 e8d9ffe7f0334cf693c3c40137bf3d7b
